sequenceDiagram
actor Customer
participant ApplicationService
participant CreditBureau
participant RiskEngine
participant NotificationService
Customer->>ApplicationService: Submit Loan Application
ApplicationService->>CreditBureau: Request Credit Report
CreditBureau->>ApplicationService: Return Credit Report
ApplicationService->>RiskEngine: Request Risk Score
RiskEngine->>ApplicationService: Return Risk Score
ApplicationService->>ApplicationService: Determine Approval Decision
ApplicationService->>NotificationService: Send Application Status Update
NotificationService->>Customer: Notify Application Status